        </ab></refsDecl></encodingDesc><revisionDesc status="proposed"><change who="MAM" when="2020-10-13">Angelegt</change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text type="letter"><body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1902_AS_RBH_1_00019"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Rich. Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb173" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Rodaun bei Lie<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ing</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb40101" type="place">Lie<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>inger Straße 2</rs>. </addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1902_AS_RBH_1_00021"/><salute>lieber Richard, </salute>ich habe mich bei <rs type="person" ref="#pmb24260">Schlichter</rs> für <hi rend="underline" n="1"><anchor xml:id="K_L1902-04-01_01_AS_Beer-Hofmann_1" type="commentary"/><date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>4</time><note xml:id="K_L1902-04-01_01_AS_Beer-Hofmann_1h" type="commentary"><ref target="1902-04-12" type="schnitzlerDiary" subtype="cf"/></note></hi> ange<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agt u Ihr wahr<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinlich kommen in Aus<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>icht ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tellt, neuen Impfstoff be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tellt.</p><p>Leider ko<c rendition="#gemination-n"/>t ich heut nicht zu Ihnen, wir mü<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en doch endlich wieder <pb facs="1902_AS_RBH_1_00022"/>einige ungehetzte Stunden miteinander verbringen find ich.</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div></body></text></TEI>